<B>Citation Corporation</B><FONT SIZE="2"> is a manufacturer of cast,
forged and machined components for the capital and durable goods
industries. Citation has approximately 5,600 employees serving <a
href="prod.html">16 divisions</a> in eight states. The company's stock is
traded on the <a href="http://www.nasdaq.com" target="_new">NASDAQ</a>
National Market under the symbol <a
href="http://www.nasdaq.com/quotes/fullquote.asp?symbol=CAST"
target="_new">CAST</a>.</FONT><br>

<br>

